channel.title: My main comp cant get onto mopar forums but laptop can?
channel.description:
hey, ive been playing moparscape on my laptop for ages now and it got really laggy with all the things i downloaded to it. so i decdided to move from my laptop to my main computer, so i downloaded moparscape client...and then i tried to get onto forums and the TOS(terms of service) came up and i typed in yes then " i agree" but instead of moving onto the forums it kept on reloading the TOS?!?!?!!?!?! please help? it would be greatly appreciated
i have also tried moparisthebest but it does the same thing
